@startuml px-toggle-update-flow
!include _standard-style.puml

title px Toggle → Status Line Update Flow

actor User as user
participant "px alias\n(~/.bash_profile)" as px
participant "proxydetox\n(launchd)" as proxydetox
participant "Health Coordinator\n(:3034)" as coordinator
participant "Status Line Cache\n(.logs/)" as cache
participant "tmux\n(status-right)" as tmux
participant "LLM Proxy\n(:12435)" as llm

== px off (disable proxy) ==

user -> px: px
activate px

px -> proxydetox: launchctl bootout\ngui/<uid>/cc.colorto.proxydetox
note right: Fully unloads the plist;\nport 3128 goes down.\nNo socket activation respawn.
deactivate proxydetox

px -> cache: rm -f combined-status-line-cache-*.txt
note right: Nuke ALL 47 per-pane\ncache files for instant\ninvalidation

px -[#43A047,dashed]-> coordinator: POST /health/refresh
activate coordinator
coordinator -> coordinator: Reset network probe age\n→ immediate re-probe
coordinator -> coordinator: Detect port 3128 down\n→ proxy_running=false
deactivate coordinator

deactivate px

... ≤5s (tmux status-interval) ...

tmux -> cache: Read cache file
note right: Cache deleted → miss
tmux -> tmux: Spawn combined-status-line.js\n(slow path, ~300ms)
tmux -> coordinator: GET /health/state
coordinator --> tmux: { proxy_running: false,\n  location: "corporate" }
tmux -> cache: Write new cache\n[P:OFF] [N:CN]
tmux --> user: **[P:OFF]** rendered\n(≤5s total latency)

... Next LLM call ...

llm -> llm: smartFetch()\n→ isProxyAlive()\n→ TCP connect 3128 fails
llm -> llm: Use directFetch\n(no proxy agent)
note right: 5s cache on probe;\nauto-switches without\nrestart or reload

== px on (enable proxy) ==

user -> px: px
activate px

px -> proxydetox: launchctl bootstrap\ngui/<uid> cc.colorto.proxydetox.plist
activate proxydetox
note right: Full plist load;\nport 3128 comes up\nvia socket activation

px -> cache: rm -f combined-status-line-cache-*.txt
px -[#43A047,dashed]-> coordinator: POST /health/refresh
activate coordinator
coordinator -> coordinator: Detect port 3128 up\n→ proxy_running=true
deactivate coordinator

deactivate px

... ≤5s ...

tmux -> coordinator: GET /health/state
coordinator --> tmux: { proxy_running: true }
tmux --> user: **[P:ON]** rendered

llm -> llm: smartFetch()\n→ isProxyAlive()\n→ TCP connect 3128 OK
llm -> llm: Use proxyFetch\n(via ProxyAgent)

@enduml
